Testimonies of Changed Lives - https://www.amazingfacts.org/news-and-features/changed-lives
 Share Your Testimony - https://www.amazingfacts.org/about-us/tell-your-story

Even though Gary was living the party scene he still had a deep desire to know God and understand the truth of His Word. He shares his story of how the truth was found.
